room_title: Escape room "Detention Bay" by Method of Escape in Fresno
room_description: You secretly arrived on the powerful space station T.I.T.A.N. (Terminate Inhabited Terrestrial Acquire Nations). Your mission is to download the TITAN blueprints to your robot. While evading enemy troops you end up in the detention bay section, weaponless and trapped in the compactor. You must get the plans of TITAN downloaded to your robot or all will be lost!
